inned on the ropes.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"image\":{\"type\":\"Asset\",\"id\":\"58vb1aQgbmKIcqkQrOcOmg\",\"title\":\"JesseRodriguezHighlgiht2\",\"file\":{\"url\":\"//images.ctfassets.net/lg76kxmf55ue/58vb1aQgbmKIcqkQrOcOmg/9cde373f4e59df2c8e423272ddefb275/JesseRodriguezHighlgiht2.jpg\",\"details\":{\"size\":128415,\"image\":{\"width\":1024,\"height\":683}},\"fileName\":\"JesseRodriguezHighlgiht2.jpg\",\"contentType\":\"image/jpeg\"}}},{\"type\":\"fighterHighlight\",\"id\":\"4jGHc1KT77jjbG9rCOk6T3\",\"title\":\"Juan Estrada KO7\",\"bodyCopy\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Rodriguez wins the junior bantamweight title, dropping Estrada in the fourth round, getting off the canvas himself in the sixth and ending the bout with a vicious left uppercut to the body.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"image\":{\"type\":\"Asset\",\"id\":\"2KjT0SnyeFErMWgLSae6wU\",\"title\":\"JesseRodriguezHighlight2\",\"file\":{\"url\":\"//images.ctfassets.net/lg76kxmf55ue/2KjT0SnyeFErMWgLSae6wU/535dc438a491bbff93403a4eb30f5c18/JesseRodriguezHighlight2.jpg\",\"details\":{\"size\":113676,\"image\":{\"width\":1296,\"height\":728}},\"fileName\":\"JesseRodriguezHighlight2.jpg\",\"contentType\":\"image/jpeg\"}}},{\"type\":\"fighterHighlight\",\"id\":\"5xrxDNjnLHBK7tvYdpn0aP\",\"title\":\"Sunny Edwards TKO9\",\"bodyCopy\":{\"nodeType\":\"document\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"Rodriguez unifies flyweight titles, scoring a knockdown to end the ninth round via overhand left. Edwards crashes face-first to the canvas and said he couldn’t see with cuts over both eyes leading to the stoppage.\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]}]},\"image\":{\"type\":\"Asset\",\"id\":\"2j8jebh8KG5PcAgELDsEqF\",\"title\":\"JesseRodriguezHighlight3\",\"file\":{\"url\":\"//images.ctfassets.net/lg76kxmf55ue/2j8jebh8KG5PcAgELDsEqF/11d190c717963259168da5718688f7bd/JesseRodriguezHighlight3.jpg\",\"details\":{\"size\":95177,\"image\":{\"width\":1024,\"height\":683}},\"fileName\":\"JesseRodriguezHighlight3.jpg\",\"contentType\":\"image/jpeg\"}}},{\"type\":\"fighterHighlight\",\"id\":\"7wYhEeFIPf2QZ7qMkxfuMz\",\"title\":\"Carlos Cuadras W12\",\"bodyCopy\":{\"nodeType\":\"document\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\",\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"nodeType\":\"text\",\"value\":\"Moving up to junior bantamweight on six days’ notice from an undercard slot, Rodriguez becomes the sport’s youngest active titlist. His power and hand speed proves to be too much as he knocks down Cuadras in Round 3.\",\"marks\":[],\"data\":{}}]}]},\"image\":{\"type\":\"Asset\",\"id\":\"3yajkxTHNVxzUePgRM8NTM\",\"title\":\"JesseRodriguezHighlight4\",\"file\":{\"url\":\"//images.ctfassets.net/lg76kxmf55ue/3yajkxTHNVxzUePgRM8NTM/bd17240a5bfc9179d70a4d0745518b1b/JesseRodriguezHighlight4.jpg\",\"details\":{\"size\":292378,\"image\":{\"width\":1442,\"height\":982}},\"fileName\":\"JesseRodriguezHighlight4.jpg\",\"contentType\":\"image/jpeg\"}}}],\"ringSays\":[{\"type\":\"ringSays\",\"id\":\"2FsurTfYX5I5tOjKg3d0vx\",\"title\":\"Heavy hitter\",\"isSmallVariant\":true,\"isLargeVariant\":false,\"largeVariationBodyCopy\":null,\"smallVariationBodyCopy\":\"Bam never disappoints. He brings rare fight-ending power to the lower weight classes.\"},{\"type\":\"ringSays\",\"id\":\"4EIR6x36LDQtlnBropj3KH\",\"title\":\"Unassuming assassin\",\"isSmallVariant\":true,\"isLargeVariant\":false,\"largeVariationBodyCopy\":null,\"smallVariationBodyCopy\":\"This soft-spoken southpaw is always respectful of opponents he ultimately dismantles.\"},{\"type\":\"ringSays\",\"id\":\"4AZ6XQrv9as6E1bAZlEJO1\",\"title\":\"Ambitious but patient\",\"isSmallVariant\":true,\"isLargeVariant\":false,\"largeVariationBodyCopy\":null,\"smallVariationBodyCopy\":\"Naoya Inoue is the opponent he dreams of facing,