ning a majority decision.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"image\":{\"type\":\"Asset\",\"id\":\"5iccJ45PELPjhtpqsP0nR3\",\"title\":\"TaylorHighlight2\",\"description\":\"\",\"file\":{\"url\":\"//images.ctfassets.net/lg76kxmf55ue/5iccJ45PELPjhtpqsP0nR3/1ea1d62ce2ebe6ec45b9cb63543cf91c/TaylorHighlight2.jpg\",\"details\":{\"size\":132504,\"image\":{\"width\":1024,\"height\":683}},\"fileName\":\"TaylorHighlight2.jpg\",\"contentType\":\"image/jpeg\"}}},{\"type\":\"fighterHighlight\",\"id\":\"01KT0nyQ7msA7uk0FAtHFQ\",\"title\":\"Delfine Persoon MD\",\"bodyCopy\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Outlasts her opponent to win a close fight and add the IBF, WBC and WBO titles to her WBA belt, making her undisputed lightweight champion.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"image\":{\"type\":\"Asset\",\"id\":\"7DeLUa9KtRLDxxxYxUR578\",\"title\":\"TaylorHighlight3\",\"description\":\"\",\"file\":{\"url\":\"//images.ctfassets.net/lg76kxmf55ue/7DeLUa9KtRLDxxxYxUR578/cdadf759173cd6eaa4ebe2a80da401de/TaylorHighlight3.jpg\",\"details\":{\"size\":131996,\"image\":{\"width\":1024,\"height\":729}},\"fileName\":\"TaylorHighlight3.jpg\",\"contentType\":\"image/jpeg\"}}},{\"type\":\"fighterHighlight\",\"id\":\"1bON5WphnjkGu33ytB3x9q\",\"title\":\"Jessica McCaskill W10\",\"bodyCopy\":{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"content\":[{\"data\":{},\"marks\":[],\"value\":\"Outboxes her opponent to win a one-sided decision in a tough fight. More importantly, it was the first time a women’s fight headlined a major card in the U.K.\",\"nodeType\":\"text\"}],\"nodeType\":\"paragraph\"}],\"nodeType\":\"document\"},\"image\":{\"type\":\"Asset\",\"id\":\"5GdxcIIi1WxNV4eeHVLUlC\",\"title\":\"TaylorHighlight4\",\"description\":\"\",\"file\":{\"url\":\"//images.ctfassets.net/lg76kxmf55ue/5GdxcIIi1WxNV4eeHVLUlC/33fcf81b8f97a5d9b878d486671c9293/TaylorHighlight4.jpg\",\"details\":{\"size\":123240,\"image\":{\"width\":1024,\"height\":701}},\"fileName\":\"TaylorHighlight4.jpg\",\"contentType\":\"image/jpeg\"}}}],\"ringSays\":[{\"type\":\"ringSays\",\"id\":\"4uSYzTDtT3kTxgHBkZgz5d\",\"title\":\"Cherry on top\",\"isSmallVariant\":true,\"isLargeVariant\":false,\"largeVariationBodyCopy\":null,\"smallVariationBodyCopy\":\"Won gold at the 2012 London Olympics in the lightweight division.\"},{\"type\":\"ringSays\",\"id\":\"5JMWwAfDz2y0mvz5yU9E3\",\"title\":\"Complete fighter\",\"isSmallVariant\":true,\"isLargeVariant\":false,\"largeVariationBodyCopy\":null,\"smallVariationBodyCopy\":\"Technically sound, can box, brawl and elite conditioning.\"},{\"type\":\"ringSays\",\"id\":\"H1zIiciM1wvD1QUFDebl4\",\"title\":\"The avenger\",\"isSmallVariant\":true,\"isLargeVariant\":false,\"largeVariationBodyCopy\":null,\"smallVariationBodyCopy\":\"Anytime a decision win has been questioned, she rematches and wins going away.\"}],\"compuboxFighterId\":\"5802\"},{\"type\":\"fighterProfile\",\"id\":\"1YdkkzbAG696YOoamTFNQ7\",\"name\":\"Claressa Shields\",\"fighterDescription\":\"Undisputed heavyweight world champion\",\"heroImage\":{\"type\":\"Asset\",\"id\":\"3gJ4jyBsECuCFUxOX8t8gy\",\"title\":\"ClaressaShields\",\"description\":\"\",\"file\":{\"url\":\"//images.ctfassets.net/lg76kxmf55ue/3gJ4jyBsECuCFUxOX8t8gy/fa0f1fc981f25c40666865f45dd73830/Claressa-Shields.png\",\"details\":{\"size\":730427,\"image\":{\"width\":1600,\"height\":900}},\"fileName\":\"Claressa-Shields.png\",\"contentType\":\"image/png\"}},\"image\":{\"type\":\"Asset\",\"id\":\"3gJ4jyBsECuCFUxOX8t8gy\",\"title\":\"ClaressaShields\",\"description\":\"\",\"file\":\"$2:props:children:1:props:children:props:children:props:children:props:children:1:props:children:props:data:header:items:1:referencedRankings:1:rankFighters:1:heroImage:file\"},\"firstName\":\"Claressa\",\"lastName\":\"Shields\",\"nickname\":\"T-Rex\",\"nationality\":{\"type\":\"nationality\",\"id\":\"3eP74Gp5askH